%% E097 - Search UI state flow - F1-10 Frontend
%% Source: docs/design/f1-10-frontend-search.md (E095)
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> idle: Component init

    idle --> loading: Submit search (query + filters)

    loading --> results: API returns results (count > 0)
    loading --> empty: API returns 0 results
    loading --> error: API error (4xx, 5xx, network)

    results --> loading: Change page / filters
    empty --> loading: Retry or change filters
    error --> loading: Retry
